WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.350 --> 02:49.990
[Episode 22]

02:50.130 --> 02:54.340
[Unbridled Pavilion]

02:59.360 --> 03:00.680
Cang Shan!

03:01.310 --> 03:02.400
Cang Shan!

03:02.960 --> 03:03.560
Coming.

03:03.560 --> 03:04.310
Cang Shan!

03:04.310 --> 03:05.120
Who is it?

03:05.800 --> 03:06.910
Cang Shan!

03:08.630 --> 03:09.590
Cang Shan!

03:10.800 --> 03:11.910
Cang Shan!

03:13.760 --> 03:15.160
Cang Shan!

03:14.660 --> 03:15.530
[Unbridled Pavilion]

03:15.180 --> 03:16.010
Cang…

03:15.910 --> 03:17.380
[Mrs. Cang, Demon Race, Stone Clan]

03:18.000 --> 03:18.800
Mother?

03:19.190 --> 03:20.610
I-It's really you.

03:20.920 --> 03:22.090
What brings you here?

03:22.310 --> 03:23.240
Cang Shan,

03:23.690 --> 03:25.620
something's happened to our Stone Clan.

03:26.600 --> 03:28.390
Mother, you came all the way here

03:28.410 --> 03:29.500
and insisted on meeting with Master.

03:29.530 --> 03:31.380
Has something serious happened in the Stone Clan?

03:32.010 --> 03:33.900
Thank you for meeting me, Master Fan.

03:33.920 --> 03:35.590
Recently, the Stone Clan has been in turmoil.

03:35.620 --> 03:36.740
Every night,

03:36.760 --> 03:38.820
members of the clan go missing and die.

03:39.770 --> 03:40.890
The bodies of the deceased

03:40.920 --> 03:42.160
will be discovered the next day

03:42.520 --> 03:44.630
in the stone forest.

03:46.710 --> 03:48.230
The details of their deaths differ,

03:48.260 --> 03:50.000
but they share one thing in common:

03:50.310 --> 03:51.470
they all died

03:51.470 --> 03:53.020
with their eyes wide open.

03:59.030 --> 04:02.290
[Cang Xuan, Demon Race, Chief of the Stone Clan]

04:02.520 --> 04:03.260
No.

04:03.280 --> 04:04.530
I need to go out and investigate.

04:04.560 --> 04:05.360
No!

04:06.030 --> 04:07.130
You can't go.

04:07.160 --> 04:08.190
You're the chief.

04:08.210 --> 04:09.330
If something happens to you,

04:09.360 --> 04:11.050
the clan will lose its backbone.

04:11.070 --> 04:12.820
Precisely because I'm the chief,

04:12.870 --> 04:14.400
I must uncover the truth

04:14.400 --> 04:15.930
and give the clan members an explanation.

04:15.950 --> 04:17.070
Then I'll go with you.

04:17.100 --> 04:19.100
No, you stay at home.

04:19.120 --> 04:20.089
What if...

04:20.630 --> 04:22.310
Cang Shan has been away from home for years.

04:23.220 --> 04:24.540
If you leave

04:24.930 --> 04:26.160
and something happens to you,

04:26.300 --> 04:28.030
you won't get to see your son

04:28.050 --> 04:29.650
ever again.

04:31.010 --> 04:32.560
It's better if he doesn't come back.

04:33.570 --> 04:35.120
The Stone Clan today

04:35.210 --> 04:37.360
is no longer the same as it used to be.

04:52.690 --> 04:54.260
Then did the chief...

04:54.750 --> 04:56.159
He never came back.

04:56.820 --> 04:58.060
I led the clan members

04:58.090 --> 04:59.650
to search every corner

04:59.670 --> 05:00.550
of the Stone Clan,

05:00.760 --> 05:02.510
but there was no trace of him.

05:02.900 --> 05:03.660
Mother.

05:05.380 --> 05:06.720
I'll go back with you to search for him.

05:08.760 --> 05:10.400
I've always been straightforward.

05:10.570 --> 05:11.570
In terms of spiritual power,

05:11.600 --> 05:13.750
only Master Fan is stronger than Cang Shan's father.

05:13.770 --> 05:15.520
Unless you go in person,

05:15.550 --> 05:16.900
if anyone else goes,

05:16.920 --> 05:18.280
I'm afraid the outcome

05:18.310 --> 05:19.390
will be the same.

05:31.510 --> 05:33.000
Why have you suddenly come back?

05:33.800 --> 05:34.560
Is something bothering you?

05:37.120 --> 05:38.310
I don't know why,

05:38.830 --> 05:40.630
but I have this inexplicable feeling of worry.

05:41.480 --> 05:42.520
I told you,

05:42.680 --> 05:43.740
as long as I'm here,

05:43.960 --> 05:45.610
you don't need to worry about anything.

05:45.690 --> 05:47.360
Members of the Stone Clan suddenly died.

05:47.680 --> 05:49.340
Cang Shan's father went missing,

05:49.560 --> 05:51.390
and his mother came straight to you for help.

05:51.850 --> 05:54.090
I know you wouldn't stand by,

05:54.110 --> 05:56.500
but I feel a sense of danger.

05:56.530 --> 05:58.040
Cang Shan calls me Master.

05:58.060 --> 05:59.330
It's natural that his mother

05:59.360 --> 06:01.100
would come to me for help.

06:01.700 --> 06:04.120
But now, you only have two stars left.

06:04.240 --> 06:06.120
It's not so easy for me to lose a star.

06:06.920 --> 06:08.390
I remember you once said

06:09.010 --> 06:10.760
you didn't want to be cowardly

06:10.790 --> 06:12.610
because of the fear of danger.

06:12.700 --> 06:13.770
But when it comes to me...

06:33.560 --> 06:34.300
Bai Shuo.

06:35.350 --> 06:37.020
The Contemplation Stone showed me another vision.

06:37.560 --> 06:38.980
I saw a village

06:39.090 --> 06:40.960
full of jagged rocks.

06:41.240 --> 06:42.680
If I'm not mistaken,

06:43.450 --> 06:44.770
the village you saw should be

06:45.050 --> 06:46.250
the village of the Stone Clan.

06:46.850 --> 06:47.920
Soon after Mrs. Cang came,

06:47.940 --> 06:49.030
the Contemplation Stone was activated.

06:49.730 --> 06:51.200
I don't think it's a coincidence.

06:51.240 --> 06:52.600
The kindness in Ning'an City,

06:52.659 --> 06:54.070
the killing in the Outlanders' City,

06:54.090 --> 06:56.430
and the love in Jingyou Mountain have all seen bloodshed.

06:56.460 --> 06:58.470
What remains are greed and hate.

06:58.990 --> 07:00.760
Both of them sound ominous.

07:00.910 --> 07:02.000
I'll go

07:02.070 --> 07:02.920
to the Stone Clan.

07:02.940 --> 07:04.010
You stay at the Unbridled Pavilion.

07:04.090 --> 07:06.860
I'm no longer the weak Bai Shuo I once was.

07:06.880 --> 07:08.510
I can go with you.

07:08.930 --> 07:10.570
You cannot afford to lose another star.

07:10.600 --> 07:11.990
Though you have power now,

07:12.010 --> 07:14.150
the Contemplation Stone won't protect you anymore.

07:14.180 --> 07:14.920
If anything happens...

07:14.920 --> 07:15.870
Since it's an "if,"

07:16.310 --> 07:17.640
it's beyond our control.

07:18.680 --> 07:20.270
I can't hide forever,

07:20.270 --> 07:22.310
never seeing anyone or doing anything.

07:22.790 --> 07:24.550
I'm not the type to run away.

07:27.580 --> 07:29.860
Besides, the more Contemplations I collect,

07:29.950 --> 07:31.600
the more power I will have.

07:32.150 --> 07:33.560
As long as I'm powerful enough,

07:33.560 --> 07:35.070
I'll be my own shield,

07:35.220 --> 07:36.330
just like you.

07:36.540 --> 07:37.810
As the Demon King of the Polar Region,

07:37.830 --> 07:39.440
when did you ever need others' protection?

07:41.490 --> 07:43.220
I can't out-argue you anymore.

07:48.760 --> 07:49.550
Master.

07:49.720 --> 07:50.480
Bai Shuo.

07:51.120 --> 07:51.890
I've made up my mind.

07:52.400 --> 07:54.130
I'll handle my clan's trouble myself.

07:54.150 --> 07:55.030
Once it's resolved,

07:55.060 --> 07:56.060
I'll reunite with you.

07:57.390 --> 07:58.640
The next Contemplation

07:58.870 --> 07:59.920
is in the Stone Clan.

08:03.220 --> 08:06.200
[Stone Clan, Demon Race]

08:32.340 --> 08:33.230
Bai Shuo,

08:33.260 --> 08:34.419
take a closer look.

08:34.440 --> 08:36.090
Is the scene you saw from here?

08:36.730 --> 08:37.610
Yes.

08:38.100 --> 08:39.220
So something big

08:39.250 --> 08:40.610
is going to happen to the Stone Clan, right?

08:40.630 --> 08:42.480
The vision only showed this place.

08:42.510 --> 08:44.510
Nothing terrifying has appeared yet.

08:44.530 --> 08:46.060
Don't panic.

08:46.710 --> 08:48.150
What are you talking about?

08:48.320 --> 08:49.240
What vision?

08:49.240 --> 08:50.320
What is going to happen?

08:50.320 --> 08:52.070
Mother, stop asking.

08:52.090 --> 08:53.400
It's hard to explain.

08:53.430 --> 08:55.000
Since I've come to the Stone Clan,

08:55.440 --> 08:57.000
I'm going to find out

08:57.330 --> 09:00.260
who's behind all these murders.

09:03.330 --> 09:04.540
Here we are.

09:09.380 --> 09:10.980
Master Fan, Ms. Bai.

09:11.000 --> 09:12.540
This place is not as good as the Unbridled Pavilion,

09:12.560 --> 09:14.970
so you'll have to make do.

09:15.000 --> 09:17.430
I'll go clean your rooms now.

09:17.450 --> 09:18.490
Thank you, Mrs. Cang.

09:25.340 --> 09:26.650
Cang Shan?

09:29.400 --> 09:30.280
Shi Lei?

09:31.620 --> 09:32.890
You've been gone for years.

09:33.320 --> 09:34.270
You're finally back.

09:34.820 --> 09:35.850
Have you learned that

09:34.920 --> 09:37.050
[Shi Lei, Demon Race, Stone Clan]

09:36.600 --> 09:38.010
something's happened in the clan?

09:38.030 --> 09:39.520
I came back too late.

09:40.780 --> 09:41.570
It's not too late.

09:41.730 --> 09:42.710
What matters is you're back.

09:43.440 --> 09:44.300
Master.

09:44.440 --> 09:45.970
This is my best friend, Shi Lei.

09:46.140 --> 09:47.690
This is the Master of Bright Moon Palace.

09:47.720 --> 09:49.120
This is Ms. Bai, a human.

09:49.940 --> 09:50.610
Master...

09:51.230 --> 09:52.320
Master of Bright Moon?

09:52.570 --> 09:53.330
Your mother said

09:53.350 --> 09:54.540
you work for Bright Moon Palace.

09:55.250 --> 09:56.250
That's actually true.

09:56.410 --> 09:58.230
Master and Ms. Bai are here to help us.

09:59.530 --> 10:00.370
Thank you, Master.

10:00.450 --> 10:01.480
Thank you, Ms. Bai.

10:01.910 --> 10:03.020
You're our guests.

10:03.050 --> 10:04.290
We should treat you with hospitality.

10:04.720 --> 10:05.790
But right now,

10:06.320 --> 10:07.320
the Stone Clan…

10:08.000 --> 10:09.000
We understand.

10:09.860 --> 10:10.980
Time is tight.

10:11.010 --> 10:12.080
Please tell Mrs. Cang to take us

10:12.120 --> 10:14.120
to see the bodies of the victims first.

10:14.630 --> 10:15.870
No need to trouble Mrs. Cang.

10:15.890 --> 10:16.930
I know where they are.

10:16.960 --> 10:17.800
I'll take you there.

10:25.010 --> 10:25.890
Master Fan.

10:25.910 --> 10:26.870
Ms. Bai.

10:27.430 --> 10:29.720
These are the bodies of the three murdered elders.

10:33.100 --> 10:33.940
I'm fine.

10:35.920 --> 10:36.960
Cang Shan,

10:36.980 --> 10:39.250
examine the cause of death and the wounds on their bodies.

10:52.330 --> 10:53.830
This one's bones are completely shattered.

11:01.260 --> 11:02.310
This one too.

11:12.630 --> 11:13.360
Master,

11:13.760 --> 11:15.580
they weren't killed in one strike.

11:15.850 --> 11:17.010
The murderer

11:17.030 --> 11:18.630
shattered their bones first,

11:18.660 --> 11:19.690
then tortured them to death.

11:21.110 --> 11:23.850
It looks like the work of a vengeful enemy.

11:24.220 --> 11:26.130
The Stone Clan has been living in the mountains for many years.

11:26.160 --> 11:27.300
We don't have any enemies.

11:27.380 --> 11:29.160
If it's not an enemy from another clan,

11:29.360 --> 11:30.640
have you considered that the killer

11:30.660 --> 11:32.160
might be from within the Stone Clan?

11:32.180 --> 11:33.070
Impossible.

11:33.090 --> 11:34.600
People here live in harmony.

11:34.620 --> 11:35.650
There has never been any conflict.

11:35.680 --> 11:37.770
No one would commit such a brutal act.

11:38.140 --> 11:39.900
Not wanting to believe it doesn't mean it's impossible.

11:40.510 --> 11:42.160
Before everything is clear,

11:43.510 --> 11:45.040
everyone is a suspect.

12:08.970 --> 12:09.750
In Ning'an City,

12:09.750 --> 12:11.100
the Outlanders' City,  and Jingyou Mountain,

12:11.130 --> 12:13.440
Young Lord saved and helped you again and again.

12:13.460 --> 12:14.460
When the Fox Clan's mission failed,

12:14.510 --> 12:15.950
she took the blame for you.

12:15.970 --> 12:17.770
Without the demonic flower armor protecting her,

12:17.800 --> 12:19.050
the punishment

12:19.070 --> 12:21.190
made her suffer far worse than before.

12:21.240 --> 12:22.550
It's not because you're so great

12:22.570 --> 12:24.620
but because Young Lord has suffered too much since childhood

12:24.650 --> 12:26.050
that she treasures the little warmth

12:26.070 --> 12:28.140
you unknowingly gave her.

12:57.390 --> 12:59.030
It's you.

12:59.050 --> 13:00.220
How do you feel?

13:09.720 --> 13:11.150
What did you make me eat?

13:11.170 --> 13:12.900
Medicine for healing and pain relief.

13:13.500 --> 13:15.100
It's a pill from Lanling?

13:15.850 --> 13:16.920
I'll take you out first.

13:18.870 --> 13:20.990
If Grand Master finds out,

13:21.120 --> 13:22.480
do you know the consequences?

13:22.600 --> 13:24.020
No matter what the consequences are,

13:24.120 --> 13:25.600
I'll take you out first.

13:26.600 --> 13:27.960
Have you thought this through?

13:28.310 --> 13:29.100
If you save me,

13:29.510 --> 13:32.090
you might be tortured by Grand Master until you're in pieces.

13:32.200 --> 13:34.650
How can I hide behind you while you take the punishment

13:34.720 --> 13:36.510
for the failed mission?

13:38.470 --> 13:39.500
You've changed.

13:40.040 --> 13:42.320
The world is full of uncertainties.

13:42.340 --> 13:43.730
Whether things change or stay the same,

13:43.760 --> 13:45.830
I'm just doing what I'm supposed to do.

13:47.740 --> 13:49.220
But I don't understand one thing.

13:49.270 --> 13:51.320
He treats you like this, making you suffer so much.

13:51.650 --> 13:53.940
Why are you still so loyal to him,

13:54.270 --> 13:55.550
still willing to risk your life for him?

13:58.000 --> 13:59.360
Those who gave birth to you

13:59.720 --> 14:01.720
despised you for being weak and sick

14:01.720 --> 14:04.030
and abandoned you in the wilderness.

14:04.410 --> 14:06.140
I pitied you,

14:06.170 --> 14:09.320
brought you back to Cold Spring Palace, and raised you.

14:10.960 --> 14:12.640
You were born useless,

14:13.000 --> 14:14.270
unable to transform

14:14.270 --> 14:15.550
or cultivate.

14:15.950 --> 14:18.430
It was also me who put in so much effort

14:18.450 --> 14:21.100
to make you who you are today.

14:39.950 --> 14:43.290
♫Across thousands of miles♫

14:43.730 --> 14:45.400
In Cold Spring Palace,

14:45.760 --> 14:47.720
only the strongest

14:47.750 --> 14:49.790
have the right to survive

14:48.020 --> 14:52.980
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

14:49.790 --> 14:51.720
and become my disciples.

14:55.470 --> 15:02.750
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

14:58.300 --> 14:59.180
Grand Master.

15:03.870 --> 15:08.910
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

15:04.490 --> 15:06.180
Living in pain

15:06.210 --> 15:08.120
is better than facing death with no escape.

15:09.090 --> 15:10.890
As long as I'm still useful to Grand Master,

15:10.910 --> 15:12.390
a little suffering

15:12.420 --> 15:13.730
is nothing.

15:14.370 --> 15:16.250
It's because of this

15:16.280 --> 15:18.400
that he tortures you again and again.

15:18.800 --> 15:20.800
If he wants to punish me, I'll accept it.

15:21.590 --> 15:22.900
I'd like to see

15:23.240 --> 15:24.270
if he wants to kill everyone

15:24.290 --> 15:25.840
who's ever risked their life for him.

15:28.430 --> 15:29.670
I'll take you out first.

15:33.120 --> 15:36.260
♫I remember that moonlit night♫

15:36.880 --> 15:39.590
♫The flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime♫

15:40.550 --> 15:44.020
♫I remember that word of concern♫

15:44.540 --> 15:47.800
♫But unfortunately, I didn't get to answer♫

15:48.370 --> 15:51.260
♫I remember that drop of tear♫

15:51.950 --> 15:55.210
♫It dried in the wind♫

15:55.800 --> 15:57.600
♫The one in the autumn wind♫

15:58.040 --> 16:01.730
♫How many times have I seen you in my dreams?♫

16:02.440 --> 16:05.770
♫That year, that year♫

16:06.700 --> 16:09.810
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

16:10.380 --> 16:13.690
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

16:13.510 --> 16:15.590
You're still carrying Lanling's medicine with you,

16:14.750 --> 16:17.270
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

16:15.620 --> 16:18.090
which makes your loyalty doubtful.

16:17.940 --> 16:21.440
♫That year, that year♫

16:18.400 --> 16:20.160
Don't do that again in the future.

16:20.930 --> 16:23.070
I just wanted to return your favors.

16:22.030 --> 16:25.180
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

16:23.670 --> 16:24.910
From now on,

16:25.360 --> 16:26.810
we are even.

16:25.690 --> 16:28.900
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

16:29.250 --> 16:30.470
Even?

16:29.940 --> 16:32.410
♫Layer after layer♫

16:30.990 --> 16:32.780
Since the moment you saved me today,

16:32.800 --> 16:34.200
our fates

16:33.380 --> 16:36.350
♫Another year passed♫

16:34.480 --> 16:35.850
in Cold Spring Palace

16:35.870 --> 16:37.430
are tied together.

16:37.930 --> 16:39.480
You're you, and I'm me.

16:40.090 --> 16:41.720
I won't stick my neck out for you again,

16:41.750 --> 16:43.470
and you don't need to take any blame for me anymore.

16:48.690 --> 16:52.200
♫I remember that moonlit night♫

16:52.620 --> 16:55.280
♫The flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime♫

16:55.360 --> 16:57.360
As Lady Fu Ling of Cold Spring Palace,

16:55.700 --> 16:59.800
♫I remember that word of concern♫

16:57.710 --> 16:59.110
you look powerful on the surface,

16:59.150 --> 17:01.360
but you've always been tormented by Zhen Yu.

17:00.500 --> 17:03.480
♫But unfortunately, I didn't get to answer♫

17:01.390 --> 17:02.910
The cold, unfeeling persona you've maintained

17:02.910 --> 17:04.270
is just your way of protecting yourself,

17:03.970 --> 17:06.839
♫I remember that drop of tear♫

17:05.000 --> 17:06.410
not your true nature.

17:06.760 --> 17:07.700
Fu Ling,

17:07.780 --> 17:10.990
♫It dried in the wind♫

17:07.890 --> 17:10.349
this kind of mere survival isn't the only way to live.

17:10.569 --> 17:11.440
You can

17:11.640 --> 17:13.200
♫The one in the autumn wind♫

17:12.190 --> 17:13.880
choose your own path.

17:13.700 --> 17:17.369
♫How many times have I seen you in my dreams?♫

17:18.480 --> 17:21.579
♫That year, that year♫

17:22.380 --> 17:23.380
Once you start

17:22.460 --> 17:25.349
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

17:23.410 --> 17:24.700
taking this medicine,

17:24.720 --> 17:25.910
you can't stop.

17:26.170 --> 17:28.400
If you stop halfway,

17:26.260 --> 17:29.600
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

17:28.700 --> 17:31.420
you'll feel pain every day.

17:30.520 --> 17:32.990
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

17:31.440 --> 17:33.020
A month after stopping taking it,

17:33.230 --> 17:35.320
the poison will take your life.

17:33.650 --> 17:37.110
♫That year, that year♫

17:36.090 --> 17:36.880
Remember,

17:37.490 --> 17:40.670
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

17:37.670 --> 17:39.030
your life

17:39.070 --> 17:40.660
is in my hands now.

17:40.690 --> 17:41.810
I can

17:41.200 --> 17:44.440
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

17:41.830 --> 17:43.420
take it back at any time.

17:45.780 --> 17:48.340
♫Layer after layer♫

17:46.580 --> 17:47.780
Chong Zhao.

17:48.720 --> 17:50.070
In this world,

17:49.140 --> 17:53.130
♫Another year passed♫

17:50.560 --> 17:53.050
not everyone has a choice.

17:56.600 --> 17:58.490
Chong Zhao, thank you.

17:58.520 --> 18:01.320
You have feelings for Young Lord,

18:01.340 --> 18:02.410
don't you?

18:02.440 --> 18:03.750
Feelings are something

18:03.770 --> 18:05.120
you can't see or touch,

18:05.150 --> 18:06.180
and they change easily.

18:06.400 --> 18:07.480
Don't jump to conclusions.

18:07.480 --> 18:09.480
You and Young Lord are both stubborn.

18:09.480 --> 18:10.270
No matter what,

18:10.270 --> 18:11.440
you saved her this time.

18:11.440 --> 18:12.960
I'll remember your kindness.

18:14.950 --> 18:15.920
No need.

18:28.010 --> 18:29.270
I've violated the palace rules

18:29.270 --> 18:30.220
and privately freed Fu Ling.

18:30.730 --> 18:31.920
Please punish me, Master.

18:32.680 --> 18:33.850
You've come

18:33.880 --> 18:35.700
sooner than I expected.

18:35.840 --> 18:37.130
I deserve punishment.

18:37.430 --> 18:38.390
All responsibility

18:38.410 --> 18:39.540
falls on me alone.

18:40.080 --> 18:41.800
I thought,

18:41.820 --> 18:43.860
in your heart, there was only Bai Shuo,

18:44.310 --> 18:45.800
but now, you seem to care for

18:45.820 --> 18:46.980
Fu Ling as well.

18:47.430 --> 18:49.000
I just didn't want to be indebted

18:49.020 --> 18:50.540
to Fu Ling anymore.

18:51.030 --> 18:52.430
I wanted to return her favors.

18:52.770 --> 18:53.830
As for whatever happens next,

18:54.330 --> 18:55.850
I'll just accept it.

18:56.880 --> 18:58.190
Are you gambling on

18:58.850 --> 19:00.480
my mercy?

19:00.680 --> 19:02.250
What makes you think

19:02.280 --> 19:03.840
I won't kill you?

19:04.140 --> 19:06.750
Because Fu Ling is already useless in your eyes.

19:07.570 --> 19:08.710
I believe

19:09.400 --> 19:11.830
you need someone stronger by your side.

19:13.060 --> 19:13.930
Who?

19:15.850 --> 19:16.920
You?

19:19.440 --> 19:21.550
I believe you have the answer.

19:22.130 --> 19:23.640
The fact that I'm still standing here,

19:23.640 --> 19:24.850
talking to you,

19:24.870 --> 19:26.980
proves that you've already

19:27.170 --> 19:28.600
made your choice.

19:32.140 --> 19:32.980
Fine.

19:33.120 --> 19:34.920
I'll let it slide this time.

19:34.950 --> 19:36.470
Go return those favors.

19:36.490 --> 19:37.690
After you're done,

19:37.720 --> 19:40.320
there are many things here

19:40.340 --> 19:41.890
that require someone like you—

19:41.920 --> 19:43.920
someone stronger—to handle.

20:29.640 --> 20:30.960
I've brought you

20:30.990 --> 20:32.790
the person you want.

20:32.820 --> 20:34.230
When will you let go of

20:34.490 --> 20:36.410
the person I want?

20:43.220 --> 20:44.690
The Stone Clan

20:44.720 --> 20:46.790
doesn't look like a demon clan at all.

20:46.820 --> 20:48.400
Life here is peaceful.

20:48.830 --> 20:50.960
How could such a creepy thing happen here?

20:51.210 --> 20:52.780
If everything in this world

20:52.810 --> 20:54.980
could be as peaceful as it appears,

20:55.050 --> 20:56.920
there wouldn't be so many injustices and killings.

20:57.870 --> 20:59.200
The two remaining Contemplations

20:59.510 --> 21:00.620
are greed and hate.

21:01.130 --> 21:03.540
In a place like the Stone Clan,

21:03.560 --> 21:04.410
do you think we'll find greed

21:04.730 --> 21:05.690
or hate?

21:06.470 --> 21:07.810
Murders out of revenge.

21:08.500 --> 21:09.890
I'd say it's hate.

21:10.440 --> 21:11.560
If it's hate,

21:12.060 --> 21:13.210
there must be a reason.

21:13.400 --> 21:14.640
If we find the root of it,

21:14.660 --> 21:15.980
perhaps we can find a solution.

21:33.620 --> 21:34.420
Mother,

21:35.120 --> 21:36.640
where did you go in the middle of the night?

21:40.250 --> 21:41.560
Where could I go?

21:41.640 --> 21:43.520
With all these family matters,

21:43.570 --> 21:45.520
I'm always bustling around

21:45.680 --> 21:47.960
and making preparations.

21:47.980 --> 21:49.950
The deaths of those victims look like an act of revenge.

21:50.110 --> 21:52.310
Mother, tell me honestly.

21:52.330 --> 21:53.330
Are their deaths

21:53.360 --> 21:55.480
related to the event back then?

21:58.640 --> 22:00.050
Stop talking nonsense!

22:00.070 --> 22:01.870
That matter happened so many years ago.

22:01.900 --> 22:03.500
If they wanted revenge, they would've come long ago.

22:03.530 --> 22:05.130
Why wait until now?

22:05.170 --> 22:06.970
Mother, do you guys all think

22:07.000 --> 22:08.090
since that matter is in the past

22:08.110 --> 22:09.220
and no one brings it up anymore,

22:09.250 --> 22:11.190
everything can be forgotten as if it never happened?

22:11.210 --> 22:13.520
We don't know if your father is still alive.

22:13.610 --> 22:15.900
I don't want to argue with you over the past.

22:16.030 --> 22:18.120
You're not allowed to bring it up again!

22:18.510 --> 22:19.800
Why not?

22:19.820 --> 22:20.860
Why not?

22:20.890 --> 22:21.930
You harmed people back then.

22:21.950 --> 22:23.910
Perhaps the consequences today are the retribution!

22:31.570 --> 22:33.690
No matter what he did back then,

22:33.810 --> 22:35.270
he is still your father.

22:40.510 --> 22:41.800
Cang Shan,

22:43.460 --> 22:45.830
your father isn't as bad as you think.

22:46.800 --> 22:48.150
As the chief,

22:48.740 --> 22:50.350
many things

22:50.660 --> 22:52.310
were beyond his control.

22:53.160 --> 22:54.670
You shouldn't speak of him like that.

22:55.740 --> 22:56.950
Now,

22:57.130 --> 22:58.580
the Stone Clan is in trouble,

22:59.030 --> 23:01.310
and your father is missing.

23:02.130 --> 23:05.330
Can't you let go of what happened back then?

23:08.150 --> 23:10.150
I'll find the murderer,

23:10.770 --> 23:11.890
and I'll find him.

23:12.750 --> 23:13.880
But back then, you indeed

23:13.880 --> 23:15.070
did something you shouldn't have.

23:15.070 --> 23:16.330
No matter how hard you try to cover it up,

23:16.350 --> 23:18.490
it won't change the fact that you did something horrible!

23:40.960 --> 23:43.300
Young Lord, I'll go make you some medicinal soup.

23:43.930 --> 23:45.370
The poison is from Grand Master.

23:45.400 --> 23:46.910
No medicine can help.

23:47.200 --> 23:48.850
At least it can ease the pain

23:48.870 --> 23:50.940
and make you look a little less pale.

23:51.030 --> 23:52.710
Do I look very pale?

23:59.240 --> 24:01.550
Young Lord, I don't understand.

24:01.550 --> 24:04.090
Why don't you tell Chong Zhao about the poisoning?

24:04.120 --> 24:05.230
It's a poison with no cure.

24:05.250 --> 24:07.050
What's the point of telling him?

24:07.680 --> 24:09.020
Would it mean one more person worrying about me,

24:09.050 --> 24:10.770
or one more person pitying me?

24:11.050 --> 24:12.520
I don't need either.

24:21.790 --> 24:22.580
It's me.

24:32.550 --> 24:34.160
Young Lord, you two talk.

24:34.160 --> 24:35.240
I'll leave.

24:45.400 --> 24:46.310
Drink it while it's hot.

24:48.510 --> 24:50.350
I'm quite curious.

24:50.380 --> 24:52.190
How come Grand Master didn't punish you?

24:52.340 --> 24:53.830
I'm already in Cold Spring Palace.

24:53.860 --> 24:56.000
He can take my life at any time.

24:58.440 --> 25:00.440
It seems Chen Ye isn't in the palace.

25:06.790 --> 25:07.880
He's physically disabled.

25:08.170 --> 25:10.190
I heard he's been making medicine and poison and studying weapons

25:10.220 --> 25:11.250
in the palace all these years.

25:11.360 --> 25:13.120
He's suddenly gone on a long trip.

25:13.540 --> 25:15.410
It looks like he has something important to do.

25:16.160 --> 25:17.480
I advise you not to inquire about it,

25:17.480 --> 25:19.900
and don't pass information to Lanling again.

25:19.930 --> 25:21.550
Every move in Cold Spring Palace

25:21.550 --> 25:23.050
is under Grand Master's watch.

25:23.080 --> 25:25.650
Just because he hasn't questioned you doesn't mean he doesn't know.

25:27.550 --> 25:28.980
What a beautiful spiritual herb!

25:29.000 --> 25:31.580
I'll take it back to help Young Lord recover.

25:35.280 --> 25:36.150
How dare you!

25:37.090 --> 25:38.680
That's a spiritual herb planted by Lord Chen Ye.

25:38.680 --> 25:39.480
Put it down!

25:39.480 --> 25:40.680
Lady Fu Ling is injured.

25:40.680 --> 25:42.010
She needs this herb.

25:42.110 --> 25:43.960
She's already fallen out of favor with Master.

25:43.960 --> 25:45.310
She doesn't deserve this herb.

25:45.310 --> 25:46.600
What are you doing?

25:47.720 --> 25:48.760
Go away!

26:06.210 --> 26:07.370
What's wrong with you?

26:08.380 --> 26:09.300
Fu Ling!

26:09.650 --> 26:10.450
Fu Ling!

26:14.780 --> 26:15.990
Why is it so hot?

26:19.500 --> 26:20.370
Fu Ling!

26:21.840 --> 26:22.630
Fu Ling.

26:30.270 --> 26:31.110
What's wrong with you?

26:37.680 --> 26:38.710
[Follow the way of heaven as the way. Practice kindness, caution, and harmony.]

26:41.160 --> 26:44.030
Follow the way of heaven as the way.

26:44.680 --> 26:45.680
Practice kindness,

26:46.750 --> 26:48.200
caution,

26:48.680 --> 26:50.160
and harmony.

26:54.310 --> 26:55.430
What did you say?

26:55.310 --> 27:00.930
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

26:55.590 --> 26:57.370
How do you know that saying?

27:00.420 --> 27:01.670
Who told you that?

27:03.610 --> 27:05.010
Who told you that?

27:03.660 --> 27:11.060
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

27:09.460 --> 27:11.260
How do you know my family motto?

27:11.980 --> 27:17.160
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

27:13.680 --> 27:14.640
Tell me!

27:14.900 --> 27:16.950
Why do you know the Chong family's motto?

27:17.550 --> 27:18.920
As an Eternal,

27:18.920 --> 27:21.080
I should follow the way of heaven as the way;

27:21.240 --> 27:23.160
practice kindness, caution,

27:23.160 --> 27:24.240
and harmony.

27:24.240 --> 27:25.640
Mother, Father,

27:25.640 --> 27:27.000
am I right?

27:27.000 --> 27:27.870
Good.

27:27.900 --> 27:29.250
You recited it correctly.

27:29.750 --> 27:31.700
This is the motto of the Chong family.

27:31.790 --> 27:34.230
As you live and cultivate as an Eternal, it's the standard to follow.

27:34.250 --> 27:35.120
Do you remember?

27:35.290 --> 27:36.560
Yes.

27:36.090 --> 27:39.800
♫Across thousands of miles♫

27:41.040 --> 27:43.160
That motto is known only by my parents and me.

27:44.310 --> 27:45.870
Do you know my parents?

27:44.420 --> 27:49.590
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

27:46.350 --> 27:47.510
What parents?

27:47.920 --> 27:49.270
I don't have parents.

27:49.270 --> 27:50.830
My parents abandoned me

27:50.830 --> 27:52.110
ten years ago.

27:52.210 --> 27:59.310
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

27:52.310 --> 27:53.460
It was Grand Master

27:53.480 --> 27:55.330
who saved me and brought me to Cold Spring Palace.

27:55.360 --> 27:56.870
Ten years ago...

27:57.570 --> 27:59.640
You came to Cold Spring Palace ten years ago?

28:00.090 --> 28:01.210
What about before that?

28:00.400 --> 28:05.280
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

28:01.480 --> 28:02.480
I don't know.

28:02.480 --> 28:03.270
What about before that?

28:03.270 --> 28:04.440
I don't know!

28:05.480 --> 28:07.660
I only have memories after coming to Cold Spring Palace.

28:08.560 --> 28:10.050
My head hurts so much.

28:08.670 --> 28:14.340
♫What kind of tree never takes root?♫

28:12.790 --> 28:13.880
That dagger...

28:15.460 --> 28:16.590
Why?

28:16.610 --> 28:18.850
Why did I see Bai Shuo's dagger again?

28:16.710 --> 28:22.170
♫What kind of roots never turn into trees?♫

28:18.870 --> 28:20.140
Those two girls…

28:20.170 --> 28:21.760
Those two girls…

28:22.410 --> 28:24.240
Who are they?

28:25.120 --> 28:32.250
♫To break the roots of love, to look at the past and seal one's heart♫

28:26.400 --> 28:27.480
The dagger...

28:29.230 --> 28:30.580
Two girls...

28:32.900 --> 28:37.750
♫I'm your wanderer♫

28:33.400 --> 28:34.480
Fu Ling,

28:34.730 --> 28:36.300
who on earth are you?

28:40.020 --> 28:40.890
How was last night?

28:40.920 --> 28:42.100
Any more victims?

28:42.380 --> 28:43.180
No.

28:43.210 --> 28:44.580
I've checked every household.

28:44.600 --> 28:45.270
Nothing happened last night.

28:45.300 --> 28:46.110
No one died.

28:46.350 --> 28:47.150
Perhaps

28:47.670 --> 28:49.720
the murderer was afraid of Master Fan

28:49.740 --> 28:50.740
and didn't dare to act.

29:07.070 --> 29:08.400
He's obviously a trouble.

29:08.400 --> 29:09.440
He's been here

29:09.440 --> 29:10.270
for a long time.

29:10.270 --> 29:12.000
Look. No one helped him.

29:12.000 --> 29:13.400
Who is he?

29:13.400 --> 29:14.790
-I don't know.
-I don't recognize him.

29:14.790 --> 29:16.230
I saw him down on the hillside

29:16.230 --> 29:17.700
when I was out gathering firewood.

29:17.880 --> 29:19.700
He must have fallen from the slope.

29:19.970 --> 29:21.500
The clan is already in trouble.

29:21.530 --> 29:22.610
We don't have the time

29:22.630 --> 29:24.020
to help an outsider.

29:24.040 --> 29:24.960
-Yeah.
-Just throw him out.

29:24.960 --> 29:25.880
Then throw him out.

29:25.880 --> 29:27.680
-Right.
-But he's still alive.

29:27.680 --> 29:28.680
Let's save him first,

29:28.680 --> 29:30.070
then kick him out.

29:30.510 --> 29:31.510
If you want to save him, go ahead.

29:31.510 --> 29:33.000
I don't want to get in trouble.

29:33.020 --> 29:33.790
Master,

29:34.060 --> 29:35.610
it's an outsider in a wheelchair

29:35.640 --> 29:36.970
who fell from the mountain.

29:37.000 --> 29:38.440
Let me check his injuries.

29:41.880 --> 29:43.200
Don't interfere.

29:43.590 --> 29:44.920
-Why save him?
-Exactly.

29:44.920 --> 29:45.920
Why help him?

29:45.920 --> 29:46.480
Mind your own business.

29:46.480 --> 29:47.350
I agree with you.

29:56.890 --> 29:59.270
We should just get rid of him, right?

30:05.620 --> 30:07.140
Guess what this is?

30:08.150 --> 30:08.940
A vessel flute?

30:10.020 --> 30:12.290
You can even play a leaf so well.

30:12.360 --> 30:14.820
I've always wanted to make you a wooden flute.

30:15.010 --> 30:16.010
Give it a try.

30:16.030 --> 30:17.780
It's definitely better than a leaf.

30:30.930 --> 30:34.090
♫I'm walking on a never-ending long road♫

30:35.050 --> 30:37.860
♫In the vast world, how can I get there?♫

30:38.990 --> 30:40.540
♫In the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped♫

30:41.130 --> 30:43.110
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

30:43.480 --> 30:46.710
♫All the feelings turned into nothing but a dream♫

30:47.280 --> 30:50.470
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

30:50.980 --> 30:54.710
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

30:55.210 --> 30:57.450
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

30:57.730 --> 30:59.520
♫Time after time♫

31:00.350 --> 31:06.550
♫Oh, melancholy♫

31:01.900 --> 31:02.970
Qi Feng?

31:13.730 --> 31:16.230
His new injuries are all external.

31:17.030 --> 31:18.220
But the spiritual veins

31:18.440 --> 31:19.810
in his legs are completely severed.

31:20.000 --> 31:22.070
It looks like a serious injury from many years ago.

31:22.440 --> 31:24.930
He must have suffered a lot these years.

31:26.040 --> 31:27.660
Don't worry too much.

31:28.110 --> 31:29.550
To see Qi Feng again

31:29.550 --> 31:30.790
is already a gift from heaven.

31:31.680 --> 31:33.440
I'll protect him well from now on.

31:35.110 --> 31:36.830
I'll go prepare a decoction for Qi Feng.

31:41.790 --> 31:43.100
Thank you.

31:43.560 --> 31:45.000
He's your brother,

31:45.090 --> 31:47.120
so I'll treat him like my own brother.

31:48.180 --> 31:49.310
Thank you.

32:06.740 --> 32:07.540
Bai Shuo.

32:07.960 --> 32:08.790
Let me do it.

32:09.920 --> 32:10.840
No need.

32:11.100 --> 32:12.620
Qi Feng is Fan Yue's brother.

32:12.700 --> 32:14.170
I must prepare this decoction myself.

32:15.110 --> 32:15.720
Then,

32:15.910 --> 32:17.560
I'll assist you from the side.

32:19.030 --> 32:19.940
Cang Shan,

32:20.070 --> 32:21.400
have there been any outsiders

32:21.400 --> 32:22.840
who fell from the mountain here before?

32:22.860 --> 32:24.170
I've been away from home for many years,

32:24.470 --> 32:25.840
so I'm not very sure.

32:25.860 --> 32:27.780
Logically speaking, the chances are small.

32:27.810 --> 32:29.240
Maybe heaven thought

32:29.260 --> 32:31.410
Qi Feng and Master had been apart for too long

32:31.500 --> 32:33.320
and made them meet here in the Stone Clan.

32:55.430 --> 32:56.230
You're awake.

32:59.270 --> 33:00.070
Who are you?

33:01.750 --> 33:02.550
Where am I?

33:03.890 --> 33:04.700
Qi Feng,

33:06.270 --> 33:07.070
I'm Yue.

33:09.230 --> 33:10.100
Yue?

33:16.660 --> 33:17.610
You're Yue?

33:19.600 --> 33:20.430
Yue!

33:37.160 --> 33:38.160
Yue.

33:39.330 --> 33:41.400
It's really you, Yue.

33:51.510 --> 33:52.480
I forgot.

33:52.550 --> 33:54.040
You're now the Demon King of the Polar Region,

33:54.060 --> 33:55.220
Master of Bright Moon.

33:55.490 --> 33:56.680
That's not appropriate.

33:57.750 --> 33:58.790
You're Qi Feng.

33:59.240 --> 34:00.310
I'm Yue.

34:00.790 --> 34:01.830
That has never changed.

34:04.710 --> 34:06.600
How did you escape from the Tiger Clan?

34:07.160 --> 34:08.650
Where have you been all these years?

34:09.370 --> 34:10.429
Back then,

34:10.690 --> 34:12.310
after I was captured by the Tiger Clan,

34:12.469 --> 34:14.159
I was locked in the dungeon.

34:14.719 --> 34:16.150
One day, there was internal strife in the Tiger Clan,

34:16.170 --> 34:17.820
and I escaped amidst the chaos.

34:18.540 --> 34:19.420
After that,

34:19.449 --> 34:20.929
I wandered from place to place.

34:23.929 --> 34:24.989
Then your legs…

34:27.020 --> 34:27.980
Who broke them?

34:30.090 --> 34:31.400
That's not important anymore.

34:31.420 --> 34:32.980
There have been too many demons who bullied me.

34:33.580 --> 34:35.230
If I remembered every one of them,

34:35.480 --> 34:37.190
there would be no hope left in living.

34:37.810 --> 34:39.050
To be honest,

34:39.199 --> 34:41.030
surviving in the demon world,

34:41.190 --> 34:42.550
where the strong prey on the weak,

34:43.040 --> 34:44.400
and only losing two legs

34:44.440 --> 34:45.760
is already good enough.

34:45.960 --> 34:47.420
Since you know I'm the Master of Bright Moon,

34:47.449 --> 34:48.920
why haven't you come to me all these years?

34:49.330 --> 34:50.650
With my weak demonic power,

34:51.440 --> 34:53.000
if I stepped into the vast

34:53.440 --> 34:54.870
Polar Region,

34:55.250 --> 34:56.960
let alone meet the Master of Bright Moon,

34:57.620 --> 34:59.460
I probably wouldn't even survive half a day.

35:01.850 --> 35:03.000
Besides,

35:03.720 --> 35:05.370
I'm a cripple now.

35:06.070 --> 35:07.950
How could I dare approach you?

35:10.410 --> 35:11.260
By the way,

35:11.290 --> 35:12.690
on the day the Baize Clan was wiped out,

35:12.710 --> 35:14.100
how did you survive?

35:15.650 --> 35:16.650
It was Grandfather.

35:18.730 --> 35:20.290
He gave me all his spiritual power.

35:20.310 --> 35:21.320
Then a few years ago,

35:21.340 --> 35:22.300
when the Tiger Clan was destroyed,

35:22.330 --> 35:23.330
was that your doing?

35:23.360 --> 35:24.670
You did that to avenge the Baize Clan,

35:24.670 --> 35:25.320
didn't you?

35:27.030 --> 35:27.880
No, it wasn't me.

35:29.620 --> 35:30.450
Why?

35:31.090 --> 35:33.470
You're the Master of Bright Moon, the strongest demon in the world.

35:33.570 --> 35:35.260
Why didn't you avenge them?

35:35.290 --> 35:36.960
I went to the Tiger Clan to seek revenge.

35:37.490 --> 35:39.300
I also went there to look for you.

35:39.320 --> 35:41.380
But by the time I arrived, the Tiger Clan had already been destroyed.

35:41.720 --> 35:42.630
I searched the entire Tiger Clan,

35:42.660 --> 35:43.830
but I couldn't find your body.

35:44.190 --> 35:45.360
All these years, I've been searching for the one

35:45.400 --> 35:46.510
who wiped out the Tiger Clan.

35:46.540 --> 35:47.360
And I've never forgotten

35:47.360 --> 35:48.900
the revenge of the Baize Clan.

35:49.790 --> 35:51.580
Nor have I ever stopped looking for you.

35:55.620 --> 35:57.350
Back then, the Tiger Clan specifically demanded you.

35:57.800 --> 35:58.920
Why was that?

36:01.730 --> 36:02.770
Some things

36:03.920 --> 36:05.290
are better left unknown.

36:05.900 --> 36:06.670
Qi Feng,

36:07.260 --> 36:08.470
we're brothers.

36:08.980 --> 36:10.980
You can tell me anything.

36:11.010 --> 36:12.970
Knowing the truth won't do you any good.

36:12.990 --> 36:14.590
It will only bring you more pain.

36:14.790 --> 36:15.830
Please, don't ask.

36:18.460 --> 36:20.530
Was what happened back then related to me?

36:22.970 --> 36:23.700
Qi Feng,

36:24.560 --> 36:25.650
tell me.

36:27.190 --> 36:28.100
I want to know.

36:29.910 --> 36:30.750
Actually,

36:31.880 --> 36:33.510
the purple-eyed boy the Tiger Clan wanted back then

36:33.510 --> 36:34.200
wasn't me.

36:34.240 --> 36:35.350
It was you.

36:36.130 --> 36:39.730
♫Don't linger, don't regret♫

36:40.550 --> 36:42.910
♫The last moonlight♫

36:43.240 --> 36:44.120
Yue.

36:43.940 --> 36:47.730
♫The water from my hometown flows gently♫

36:44.330 --> 36:45.350
Yue.

36:45.890 --> 36:46.600
Yue.

36:46.630 --> 36:48.130
Let's go out and play.

36:48.730 --> 36:51.430
♫Sending me to the distant place♫

36:52.050 --> 36:56.130
♫In this life, at this time♫

36:52.450 --> 36:53.550
What's wrong?

36:53.580 --> 36:55.650
You were born with purple eyes.

36:55.860 --> 36:57.540
Even though you never said it,

36:56.400 --> 36:59.950
♫I dare not look back♫

36:58.330 --> 37:01.120
I knew it had always bothered you.

37:00.650 --> 37:04.020
♫Is there the same moonlight♫

37:01.550 --> 37:02.760
Later,

37:02.960 --> 37:05.290
I secretly learned a technique to swap eyes

37:05.050 --> 37:08.100
♫On your path?♫

37:06.370 --> 37:07.990
and switched your purple eyes

37:08.230 --> 37:09.900
with mine.

37:08.930 --> 37:11.970
♫I'm walking on a never-ending long road♫

37:09.990 --> 37:10.880
See?

37:10.900 --> 37:11.820
Aren't I amazing?

37:12.500 --> 37:15.970
♫In the vast world, how can I get there?♫

37:12.960 --> 37:14.130
Not long after,

37:14.590 --> 37:16.320
Grandfather discovered what I had done.

37:16.620 --> 37:18.480
♫In the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped♫

37:19.110 --> 37:20.960
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

37:20.880 --> 37:21.760
Yue,

37:21.220 --> 37:24.200
♫All the feelings turned into nothing but a dream♫

37:21.780 --> 37:24.360
why didn't you ever tell me

37:24.380 --> 37:27.430
that you didn't like your purple eyes?

37:24.750 --> 37:28.080
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

37:27.540 --> 37:29.620
Grandfather, I'm sorry.

37:28.730 --> 37:32.010
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

37:29.720 --> 37:30.470
I...

37:30.890 --> 37:31.740
Grandfather,

37:32.170 --> 37:33.880
it was my idea to swap eyes with Yue.

37:32.450 --> 37:34.930
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

37:33.900 --> 37:35.090
It's not his fault.

37:35.500 --> 37:36.960
♫Time after time♫

37:35.630 --> 37:37.080
What's done is done.

37:37.590 --> 37:42.640
♫Oh, melancholy♫

37:38.280 --> 37:40.730
Perhaps it's fate.

37:41.190 --> 37:43.630
Now that you've exchanged eyes,

37:44.290 --> 37:46.170
they can't be restored.

37:46.680 --> 37:49.130
Purple eyes are a natural gift

37:49.560 --> 37:52.480
and never meant to be forcibly changed.

37:52.850 --> 37:54.170
Since you two

37:54.190 --> 37:56.640
have already made the exchange,

37:57.140 --> 37:58.560
I will temporarily

37:58.590 --> 38:00.180
conceal Qi Feng's

38:00.200 --> 38:02.520
eye color.

38:02.930 --> 38:04.410
I hope that in the future,

38:04.430 --> 38:06.120
both of you

38:06.150 --> 38:08.550
can be safe and sound.

38:09.550 --> 38:12.590
♫I'm walking on a never-ending long road♫

38:10.160 --> 38:11.840
Why don't I remember any of this?

38:12.670 --> 38:14.710
It happened when you were 14.

38:13.120 --> 38:16.370
♫In the vast world, how can I get there?♫

38:15.000 --> 38:15.980
Have you forgotten?

38:16.460 --> 38:19.110
At 15, you fell from a cliff

38:17.240 --> 38:19.100
♫In the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped♫

38:19.750 --> 38:21.580
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

38:20.060 --> 38:21.820
and lost all your previous memories.

38:21.950 --> 38:24.460
♫All the feelings turned into nothing but a dream♫

38:22.800 --> 38:24.230
Then why didn't you tell the truth

38:24.230 --> 38:25.320
when the Tiger Clan came

38:25.200 --> 38:28.730
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

38:25.320 --> 38:26.410
looking for the purple-eyed boy?

38:26.440 --> 38:27.320
And why didn't Grandfather…

38:27.320 --> 38:28.190
Because Grandfather and the rest of the clan

38:28.190 --> 38:29.710
had already made their choice.

38:29.120 --> 38:32.590
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

38:31.660 --> 38:33.040
What could I do?

38:33.070 --> 38:35.390
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

38:35.850 --> 38:37.450
♫Time after time♫

38:38.210 --> 38:44.400
♫Oh, melancholy♫

39:09.890 --> 39:10.690
Fan Yue!

39:28.120 --> 39:29.930
You don't need to say anything.

39:31.030 --> 39:32.710
Calm down first.

39:38.550 --> 39:40.720
So, I'm the purple-eyed boy.

39:42.480 --> 39:44.490
The one the Tiger Clan wanted to capture back then was me.

39:44.590 --> 39:47.930
♫The person standing far away♫

39:48.540 --> 39:49.840
How could that be?

39:48.940 --> 39:51.310
♫Don't be afraid♫

39:50.150 --> 39:51.230
Then Grandfather

39:51.460 --> 39:52.920
and the Baize Clan…

39:51.650 --> 39:56.370
♫The stars will guide you to me♫

39:52.950 --> 39:54.460
Grandfather and the clan stayed silent

39:54.480 --> 39:56.040
in order to protect me.

39:56.250 --> 39:58.160
They all chose to sacrifice Qi Feng.

39:57.210 --> 40:03.600
♫Walk towards me♫

39:59.920 --> 40:00.710
Bai Shuo,

40:02.510 --> 40:03.670
who am I really?

40:04.130 --> 40:06.240
What does being the purple-eyed boy mean?

40:05.530 --> 40:08.280
♫My heart feels so...♫

40:06.680 --> 40:09.110
Why did everyone sacrifice themselves for me?

40:08.720 --> 40:14.540
♫It's pounding as I wait for you♫

40:09.540 --> 40:10.940
Everything I have now

40:11.080 --> 40:13.000
was bought with Qi Feng's suffering

40:13.030 --> 40:13.760
and pain.

40:16.540 --> 40:20.430
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

40:19.300 --> 40:21.530
Don't put all the blame on yourself.

40:22.950 --> 40:24.470
No matter who you are,

40:24.040 --> 40:27.390
♫You are my distant call♫

40:25.100 --> 40:27.230
you were innocent back then.

40:27.570 --> 40:29.610
Do you remember what Grandfather told you

40:27.870 --> 40:32.340
♫You are my first and last♫

40:29.640 --> 40:30.730
before he passed away?

40:31.190 --> 40:32.920
He told you to live well.

40:33.070 --> 40:39.160
♫My heart is trembling for you♫

40:34.820 --> 40:36.090
One day,

40:36.400 --> 40:38.020
you'll understand who you are.

40:38.980 --> 40:41.580
You can't let Qi Feng's sudden return

40:39.580 --> 40:42.470
♫In this moment where we embrace each other♫

40:41.600 --> 40:43.520
erase all the pain you've endured

40:42.950 --> 40:47.000
♫Let's never let go♫

40:43.550 --> 40:45.240
and all the effort you've made.

40:46.760 --> 40:48.270
What we need to do now

40:48.290 --> 40:50.570
is uncover the truth behind everything,

40:50.740 --> 40:52.490
protect those who need protecting,

40:52.970 --> 40:54.260
and keep living.

40:54.620 --> 40:56.080
That's what Grandfather

40:56.150 --> 40:57.510
would want to see the most.

41:05.100 --> 41:10.090
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

41:12.540 --> 41:16.530
♫You are the light I yearn for♫

41:17.120 --> 41:22.090
♫You are my determined way home♫

41:21.630 --> 41:23.420
She came to Cold Spring Palace ten years ago.

41:23.450 --> 41:24.860
She knows my parents

41:24.880 --> 41:26.500
and the Chong family's motto.

41:27.300 --> 41:28.610
More importantly,

41:28.720 --> 41:30.770
she has memories of Bai Shuo's dagger.

41:31.260 --> 41:32.180
Could it be…

41:32.640 --> 41:35.150
she's Bai Xi, who went missing ten years ago?

41:35.480 --> 41:38.870
Follow the way of heaven as the way.

41:39.350 --> 41:40.540
Practice goodness,

41:41.280 --> 41:42.840
caution,

41:43.400 --> 41:44.920
and harmony.

41:48.170 --> 41:49.920
If Fu Ling really is Bai Xi,

41:49.950 --> 41:51.160
after she killed Uncle Bai

41:51.180 --> 41:52.710
and has repeatedly tried to kill Shuo,

41:53.200 --> 41:55.430
how could she possibly face the truth?

41:56.280 --> 41:57.850
And for Shuo,

41:58.220 --> 42:00.510
if she learns that the sister she's been missing every day

42:00.600 --> 42:02.570
is actually the person she hates most,

42:02.900 --> 42:04.690
how will she accept it?

42:05.400 --> 42:06.810
But Bai Xi was a human,

42:06.840 --> 42:08.220
while Fu Ling is a demon.

42:08.430 --> 42:09.840
Why is that?

42:11.120 --> 42:13.290
Fu Ling's identity isn't fully confirmed yet.

42:13.490 --> 42:14.760
Telling Master now

42:14.790 --> 42:15.910
might be too soon.

42:17.010 --> 42:18.710
I hope I'm wrong.

42:20.010 --> 42:21.810
A truth so cruel

42:22.450 --> 42:24.590
might as well remain a mystery forever.

42:30.840 --> 42:31.630
Sect Leader,

42:32.110 --> 42:33.030
you want to see me?

42:34.960 --> 42:36.030
I haven't received

42:36.030 --> 42:37.880
any word from Chong Zhao in some time.

42:37.880 --> 42:40.110
I wonder how things are going on his side.

42:40.510 --> 42:43.250
The last time you saw that evil insect in Ning'an City,

42:43.550 --> 42:45.110
it was almost fully grown.

42:45.770 --> 42:47.250
By now, it's probably

42:47.270 --> 42:49.010
already fully grown.

42:49.080 --> 42:50.520
I've already notified other Eternal sects.

42:50.540 --> 42:53.310
Their disciples have strengthened daily patrols and inspections.

42:53.340 --> 42:55.080
No trace of the evil insect has been found.

42:55.280 --> 42:56.780
I wonder what that old dragon from Cold Spring Palace

42:56.810 --> 42:58.800
intends to do with the evil insect.

42:58.830 --> 43:02.630
The evil insect was created by Chen Ye from Cold Spring Palace.

43:02.650 --> 43:05.810
It's said that he's highly skilled in weaponry and poison-making.

43:06.550 --> 43:07.880
I'm worried...

43:08.440 --> 43:09.920
Sect Leader, are you worried

43:09.920 --> 43:11.190
that once the evil insect is unleashed,

43:11.210 --> 43:11.960
its harm

43:11.990 --> 43:13.820
may rival the Nether Poison from back then?

43:14.370 --> 43:16.570
I hope I'm overthinking it.

43:20.710 --> 43:22.670
May what I fear

43:22.690 --> 43:24.810
never come to pass.

43:37.710 --> 43:38.500
Come in.

43:43.510 --> 43:44.530
You are…

43:44.550 --> 43:45.430
Bai Shuo.

43:45.460 --> 43:46.460
You're injured.

43:46.510 --> 43:47.550
I've brought some pills

43:47.550 --> 43:48.550
specifically for you.

43:49.940 --> 43:51.310
You're a physician?

43:51.340 --> 43:52.840
I'm Fan Yue's friend,

43:53.070 --> 43:54.230
and I know a little about medicine.

43:54.600 --> 43:55.640
These pills

43:55.880 --> 43:57.360
will help with your injuries.

43:57.800 --> 43:59.760
That's very thoughtful of you. Thank you.

43:59.880 --> 44:02.010
While you were unconscious, I examined your injuries.

44:02.400 --> 44:04.400
Your recent wounds are all external

44:04.400 --> 44:05.820
and will heal quickly.

44:05.850 --> 44:07.720
As for your legs,

44:08.210 --> 44:09.920
I don't have a way to treat them right now.

44:09.950 --> 44:10.950
I know.

44:11.320 --> 44:12.510
My spiritual veins are all severed.

44:12.540 --> 44:13.620
No medicine can help.

44:14.150 --> 44:15.670
That's what the previous physicians said too.

44:16.030 --> 44:16.830
It's fine.

44:16.900 --> 44:18.090
I'm used to it.

44:18.120 --> 44:19.330
Thank you for your concern.

44:20.560 --> 44:22.290
Since you're Yue's friend,

44:22.320 --> 44:23.720
then you're also my friend.

44:25.780 --> 44:27.010
I don't have much to give,

44:27.040 --> 44:28.330
just a few small handmade things.

44:28.560 --> 44:30.710
I made this bamboo dragonfly myself.

44:30.840 --> 44:32.570
I'd like to give it to you as a thank-you gift.

44:36.780 --> 44:39.020
It's not as precious as these pills,

44:39.130 --> 44:40.360
but it's a token of my appreciation.

44:40.960 --> 44:42.390
It looks delicate.

44:42.830 --> 44:44.170
I'm glad you don't find it too simple.

44:46.920 --> 44:48.250
Is Yue okay?
